description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, some conservatives are condemning the movement to pardon Derek Chauvin. They say that BLM will be mad if we pardon him. And, of course, we should never do anything that might make BLM mad. Also, a CNN commentator claims that Ukrainians are more American than Americans. A drag queen shows up to protest a law in Texas but only ends up proving why the law is necessary. And a woman on a reality TV dating show leaves her fiancé at the altar because he isn’t woke enough.
